latestReleaseNotes:
### Release info
Oobee is available as a desktop app for Mac and Windows. The setup files can be downloaded under `Assets` at the bottom of the page.

### Installation Guide
* Refer to the [Installation Guide](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/blob/master/INSTALLATION.md) for Windows and Mac.

### What's New
#### Features
- [Adds reason for unscanned pages in report HTML](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/commit/4632a8397c79404ecf6db892265fb12856979562)
- [Up to 41% faster with new concurrency algorithm](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/commit/1446e082e04d2c6cea7b8e71f1994b03a3b18e19)

#### Bug fixes
- [Fixes email clients and other app intent pop-ups when crawling websites](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/commit/f8f28edf16d4243f070c37c9fa806f242a6ae15c) and [here](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/commit/7d1383d1d70ad057584ae9ef38a543094420624c)
- [Updates package version in transient dependencies](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/commit/e17f735f1adf79ab9248b9f03239e58c8d1e1029) and [here](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/commit/b1369f5650852b75bb1b237be557a3bd5c17ac07)
- [Fixes axe-core inaccurately flagged elements as Must Fix < 24px target-size](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/commit/59c3c3a28fb9457621b3d6c6743f75fedd53abe4)
- [Fixes miscalculated WCAG Pass Percentage and broken link to WCAG 2.1.3 when scrollable-region-focusable rule findings](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee/commit/d34f1b0ef1157f7b70660be14b747173365cb47e)
- [Fix intermittent scan complete emits No pages were scanned on Windows app](https://github.com/GovTechSG/oobee-desktop/commit/7d995225e76ac459087e37a2f00ce46fca98004e)
